  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Appearance Override</span>.<br><br>A robust and well-made covering: waterproof, windproof and designed to keep the wearer protected against anything they may encounter while exploring unmapped worlds.<br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">套装外观</span>。<br><br>做工精细的牢固斗篷：不光防水、防风，还能够帮助穿戴者抵御在探索未知世界时遇到的各种危害。<br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>使用以更改你的套装外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "獨特的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝外觀覆寫</span>。<br><br>製作精良的耐用覆蓋物：防風防水，穿戴者探索未知世界遭遇任何意外時能提供保護。<br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>改變你的強化套裝外觀。"
  },
